OASISFormat: 0.3
Name:        io-page
Version:     1.0.0
Synopsis:    Core platform libraries for Mirage (UNIX and Xen).
             This provides the `OS` library which handles timers,
             device setup and the main loop, as well as the runtime
             for the Xen microkernel.Page-aligned memory allocator.
Authors:     Anil Madhavapeddy, David Scott, Thomas Gazagnaire
License:     ISC
